latestPosts.caption:
Ananya Birla (@ananyabirla) thrives as a creator across multiple dimensions—whether it’s singing, songwriting, or venturing into new business arenas. Known for crafting subtle yet impactful social media campaigns, she always keeps her followers guessing what’s next. Embracing the power of originality, Ananya steps into the Beauty and Personal Care market with LOVETC, her own multi-brand retail chain offering high-performance, affordable beauty and self-care products. Meet our April-May cover star, captured in her boss-babe vibe at her stunning bungalow.

Editor-in-Chief: Ruchika Mehta (@ruchikamehta05)
Photographer: Sasha Jairam (@sashajairam)
Interview: Sangeeta Waddhwani (@sindhycrawford)
Creative Director: Avantikka Kilachand (@avantikkak)
Senior Fashion Stylist: Anushree Sardesai (@anushree_sardesai)
Ananya’s Stylist: Toshia Kader (@toshia_kader)
Cover Design: Mandeep Singh Khokhar (@mandy_khokhar19)
Editorial Coordinator: Shalini Kanojia (@shalinikanojia)
Make-up and Hair Artist: Loveleen Ramchandani (@loveleen_makeupandhair)
Assistant Photographer: Jagan Khursule (@jagan_khursule)

Ananya is wearing a shirt from Massimo Dutti (@massimodutti) and jeans from Acne Studios (@acnestudios); jewellery, Ananya’s own; Cartier (@cartier) timepiece and rings from The Pairs (@thepairsjewels).
